  "lineCount": 146,
  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "The Military-Industrial comp",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "through the use of psycho-politics (brainwashing by",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "controlled news management).",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "Consider this: In order to survive, a commer-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "cial medium, such as a newspaper or magazine,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "requires a vast amount of advertising revenue. The",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "mere subscription fees will not cover the costs.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Thus, they depend for their continued existence upon",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "money paid by advertisers. Suppose, then, that the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "editor of a certain newspaper decides that he is",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "opposed to the Vietnam policy, and says so in his",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "paper. The advertisers simply say to the editor,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "\"Either you toe the mark and print what we want, or",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "we'll withdraw our advertising.\"",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Such pressures are a fact of life. The newsmen",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "are torn between their higher devotion to Truth, and",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "also to the lower level of their physical needs.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Rather than jeopardize their security and their",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "futures they, of course, submit meekly to power.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Their actions are fully understandable, and we do not",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "hold them responsible.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "We throw the blame directly on the Military-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "Industrial complex which, by its underhanded dealing,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "threats of force, and economic pressure and retali-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "ation, has crushed the spirit of American journalism",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "and turned it from a dynamic motivating force in",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "American life into a weak-willed, subservient",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "mouthpiece for the power-masters. We blame them",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "for the death of journalistic freedom and individuality!",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "One more comment on this topic: May I say that",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "a better economic system is already known to the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "leaders of the Flying Saucer Movement. It is the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "system known as Universal Economics. As we have",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "said over and over before, it is the non-money",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "economic system which MUST be applied on your",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "planet before you can start to resolve most of your",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "major problems and thus begin to establish a highly-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "advanced, non-destructive state of existence on",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "Earth, such as we of more advanced planets have",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "enjoyed for so long. INVESTIGATE THIS SYSTEM",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "to evaluate it for its merit - then ACT to apply it!",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "YOUR VERY SURVIVAL AS A CIVILIZATION MAY",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "DEPEND UPON IT!",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "Perhaps this is an opportune time to clarify a",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "few questions which have been asked about us.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "Do we of Korendor work with the local planets",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "in our operations? Yes, we do cooperate with them",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "a great deal. However, our work on Earth is",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "relatively independent of the local planets. We have",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "many times overstepped what is considered to be the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "limit of interference upon other planets. This has",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "caused a good deal of debate between them and us.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "Each time we have pointed out that we of Korendor",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "are basically pragmatic in nature. Although we do",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "respect the laws of self-destiny, we feel also that",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "where state of disaster, it is our right and our duty to",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "do so. We have interfered in such places as the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "United States, China, Russia, and on a large scale in",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "Vietnam. This has caused no end of consternation in",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "the local Tribunal of Planets. We are sympathetic to",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "their viewpoint, but we do feel that their policy is",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "limited in its capacity to achieve the desired goals.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "It is our opinion that one cannot stand on the sidelines",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "and achieve any noticeable results.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "As I have said before, we have infiltrated your",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "planet. We are directly involved in Earth's life.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "You might say that you have been invaded - a strong",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "way of phrasing it, to be sure, but nonetheless",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "factual, since we walk and work amongst you daily!",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "text": "We have been asked about our physical appear-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "text": "ance. We are humanoid, indistinguishable from",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "text": "yourselves, except that in our natural form we aver-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "text": "age three to four feet in height. Every other dimen-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 74,
      "text": "sion is proportionately scaled.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "text": "We are able to increase our height when on",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "text": "Earth through a technical process related to repro-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "text": "duction. It is concerned with recording the molecular",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "text": "structures of our bodies, and then projecting them",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 79,
      "text": "identically on a larger scale. The molecules in our",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "text": "internal structure are adjusted by a computer which",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "text": "controls the reproducer.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 82,
      "text": "Our most common skin color is a little darker",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 83,
      "text": "than yours, although we have skin colors which match",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 84,
      "text": "yours do all over the Earth. Usually, people would",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "text": "look \"tan\" to you. We are NOT heliotrope, as has",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 86,
      "text": "been suggested!",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 87,
      "text": "Concerning our language, we generally speak",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "text": "two tongues and we are fairly familiar with yours.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89,
      "text": "In Korendor itself we speak the native language,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 90,
      "text": "Korendian. It is similar in many ways to your",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 91,
      "text": "languages since it, like yours, was originally taken",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 92,
      "text": "from Galingua, one of the two universal tongues. The",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "text": "other is Solex Mal, which is more familiar to you,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 94,
      "text": "since it is used by your local Solar System planets.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 95,
      "text": "It is seldom heard now in our sector of space, as",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 96,
      "text": "Galingua has replaced it almost entirely.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 97,
      "text": "Unlike your own, however, the Korendian",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 98,
      "text": "language is very rhythmic, and has many pleasant",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 99,
      "text": "and beautiful sounds, such as \"g\" or \"z\". Some",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 100,
      "text": "sharper sounds like \"c\" and \"k\" are minimized. It is a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 101,
      "text": "beautiful language which is very musical and pleasant",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 102,
      "text": "to hear.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 103,
      "text": "Perhaps you would be surprised to learn that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 104,
      "text": "ancient Latin was liberally taken from Galingua.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 105,
      "text": "There are many similarities in the two languages, and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 106,
      "text": "modern English has roots on other worlds.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 107,
      "text": "In concluding my message to you, may I say to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 108,
      "text": "people of Earth: open up your minds and your hearts",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 109,
      "text": "to the world around you. There is so much to be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 110,
      "text": "learned, so much to be discovered. Don't spend",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 111,
      "text": "precious hours and days in bigotry and ignorance,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 112,
      "text": "and in senseless fighting and killing. To do so is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 113,
      "text": "truly a crime against nature and humanity.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 114,
      "text": "At this stage where you have the very answer",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 115,
      "text": "almost in your grasp, how irrational and barbaric it",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 116,
      "text": "is to spend futile hours warring with your brothers!",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 117,
      "text": "As an old saying on your world puts it: \"As you make",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 118,
      "text": "your bed, so shall you lie in it.\" The decision does not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 119,
      "text": "seem difficult. Here are the alternatives: a world",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 120,
      "text": "living in harmony, justice, security and abundance",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 121,
      "text": "for all, or a world continuing to reap bloody harvests",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 122,
      "text": "that grow from the seeds of mistrust. If left to their",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123,
      "text": "own devices, the majority of mankind will forge onward",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124,
      "text": "to a destruction and annihilation, oblivious to their",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 125,
      "text": "actions. They are short-sighted; they have no regard",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 126,
      "text": "for the future.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 127,
      "text": "It is you New Age people, dedicated to the welfare",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128,
      "text": "of all mankind, and having the vision and understanding",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129,
      "text": "of the ways to build the better world of tomorrow,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 130,
      "text": "who must lead the way. You have the future in YOUR",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 131,
      "text": "hands, if you will but shoulder your responsibilities.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 132,
      "text": "The Flying Saucer Movement, as you call it, belongs",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 133,
      "text": "to you. Support it in every way possible. Help it to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 134,
      "text": "grow until it is influential throughout your world. Go",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 135,
      "text": "out into the world and find the misguided, find the lost,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 136,
      "text": "and reclaim them. We are behind you all the way. As I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 137,
      "text": "said many times before, we will take two steps for every",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 138,
      "text": "one that you take to help yourselves.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 139,
      "text": "The time has come for nations to \"bury the hatchet\",",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 140,
      "text": "to clasp hands, and plunge into the future together -",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141,
      "text": "in co-operation toward mutual goals. Look to the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 142,
      "text": "heavens and realize that you are not in bleak atomic",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 143,
      "text": "desolation, but in the great greatness that you can",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 144,
      "text": "achieve if you will work for it. Choose the right path",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 145,
      "text": "and you will qualify to join with us in our journeys among",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 146,
      "text": "the stars.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    }
  ],
  "blockCount": null
}
